John. You come here today? Seriously?

275
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,080
Mark?

276
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,640
Mark.

277
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,840
Oh, dear.

278
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:37,400
