296
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,800
afraid of.

297
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:50,360
I didn't talk to you,
but at least I didn't lie.

298
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:54,320
Okay? Like I am not lying now.
