329
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,560
Young women, mostly.

330
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:10,840
Wow, young women?

331
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:13,680
Even stuff like this?

332
00:25:14,280 --> 00:25:15,760
Peter Kurten,

333
00:25:15,840 --> 00:25:17,960
